<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Pending Review - Soda City Outdoors</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/styles.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background: #f8fafc;
        }
        .pending-section {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 4rem auto;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .pending-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #17a2b8;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .alert-box {
            background: #d1ecf1;
            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
            color: #0c5460;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="pending-section">
        <div class="pending-icon">‚è≥</div>
        <h1 class="mb-4">Account Pending Review</h1>
        
        <div class="alert-box">
            <h4>Your reinstatement request is being reviewed</h4>
            <p class="mb-0">We have received your request to reinstate your account and it is currently under review.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mb-4">
            <h5>What happens next:</h5>
            <ul class="text-start">
                <li>Our team will review your account and payment history</li>
                <li>We may contact you for additional information</li>
                <li>Once approved, your account will be reactivated</li>
                <li>You'll receive an email notification when complete</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mb-4">
            <h5>Review timeline:</h5>
            <ul class="text-start">
                <li>Standard review: 1-3 business days</li>
                <li>Complex cases: Up to 1 week</li>
                <li>You'll be notified of any delays</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="d-grid gap-2">
            <a href="mailto:scoadmin@sodacityoutdoors.com" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
                <i class="fas fa-envelope me-2"></i>Contact Support
            </a>
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">
                Return to Homepage
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-4 text-muted">
            <small>
                <strong>Support Email:</strong> scoadmin@sodacityoutdoors.com<br>
                <strong>Review Status:</strong> In Progress
            </small>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 